<item>
            <title>[PIG-3929] pig.temp.dir should allow to substitute vars as hadoop configuration does</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3929</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;pig.temp.dir should allow substituting system variables so that it can be configured to have user level temp directory, if required.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
